void calcgradConstraintDetQ ( const SlaterDet *  Q,
const SlaterDetAux *  X,
const gradSlaterDetAux *  dX,
gradSlaterDet *  ddetq 
)

Definition at line 747 of file ConstraintQuadrupole.c.

References calcCMPosition(), calcgradSlaterDetOBME(), calcSlaterDetOBME(), dim, par, quadrupolepara::q, SQR, gradSlaterDet::val, and quadrupolepara::Xcm.

{
  double Xcm[3];
  double q[9], detq, adjq[9];

  int i;
  quadrupolepara q2par;

  calcCMPosition(Q, X, Xcm);

  OneBodyOperator op_ob_q = {dim: 9, opt: 1, par: Xcm, me: ob_quadrupole};

  calcSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, &op_ob_q, q);

  for (i=0; i<3; i++)
    q2par.Xcm[i] = Xcm[i];

  detq = det(q);
  adjunct(q, adjq);

  for (i=0; i<9; i++)
    q2par.q[i] = 1.0/(3*SQR(cbrt(detq)))*adjq[i];

  gradOneBodyOperator gop_ob_detq = {opt: 1, par: &q2par, me: gob_quadrupole};

  calcgradSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, dX, &gop_ob_detq, ddetq);
  ddetq->val = cbrt(detq);
}

void calcgradConstraintEQ2 ( const SlaterDet *  Q,
const SlaterDetAux *  X,
const gradSlaterDetAux *  dX,
gradSlaterDet *  dq2

Definition at line 583 of file ConstraintQuadrupole.c.

References calcCMPosition(), calcgradCMSlaterDetOBME(), calcgradSlaterDetOBME(), calcSlaterDetOBME(), dim, par, quadrupolepara::q, SQR, gradSlaterDet::val, and quadrupolepara::Xcm.

{
  double Xcm[3];
  double q[9], qsq = 0.0;

  int i;
  quadrupolepara q2par;

  calcCMPosition(Q, X, Xcm);

  OneBodyOperator op_ob_q = {dim: 9, opt: 1, par: Xcm, me: ob_equadrupole};

  calcSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, &op_ob_q, q);

  for (i=0; i<9; i++)
    qsq += SQR(q[i]);
  
  for (i=0; i<3; i++)
    q2par.Xcm[i] = Xcm[i];
  for (i=0; i<9; i++)
    q2par.q[i] = q[i]/sqrt(qsq);

  gradOneBodyOperator gop_ob_q2 = {opt: 1, par: &q2par, me: gob_equadrupole};

  calcgradSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, dX, &gop_ob_q2, dq2);

  OneBodyOperator gcmop_ob_q2 = {dim: 6, opt: 1, par: &q2par, me: gcmob_equadrupole};

  calcgradCMSlaterDetOBME(Q, X, dX, &gcmop_ob_q2, dq2);
  dq2->val = sqrt(qsq);
}
